)

See CHANGELOG for current test counts per release.

== Testing Philosophy

- *Test behavior, not implementation* — tests verify observable behavior.
- *One assertion per concept* — each test validates one logical concept.
- *Descriptive names* — test names describe what is being tested.
- *No mocking core types* — Result, Option, Either are tested directly.
- *SPARK verification* — domain types are verified with GNATprove.

