= Test Maintenance

== When to Update

- *New operation added*: add tests for the new operation.
- *Behavior changed*: update affected tests.
- *Bug fixed*: add a regression test.
- *API signature changed*: update test instantiations.

== Quality Guidelines

- Each public operation should have at least one test.
- Test both success and failure paths.
- Test edge cases (empty values, boundary conditions).
- Keep tests independent (no shared mutable state).

== Continuous Integration

Tests run automatically on:
- pull request creation,
- push to main branch, and
- release tag creation.
